---
import { ImagesRoute } from "../../assets/images/ImagesRoute";
import { ViewMoreButton } from "../../components/buttons";
import {SectionTitle} from "../../components/typographys"
---

<SectionTitle label="Technology" explain="技術選定(技術者向け)"/>
<section class="section-frame technology-section">
    <p class="text-5xl">
        軽量マイコン×モダン開発スタックを組み合わせた、<br/>
        リアルタイム性重視の IoT システム構成
    </p>
    <div class="technology-section__inner">
        <div>
            <p class="concept-text-width">小型 IoT デバイス（ESP32C3）を MQTT でクラウド（ASP.NET Core）と連携させ、その上で .NET MAUI Blazor Hybrid を使ってクロスプラットフォームな UI を提供する、リアルタイム性と開発効率を重視したモダンな IoT アーキテクチャを採用。</p>
            <ViewMoreButton label="ViewMore" path="/technology" />
        </div>
        <div class="technology-section__panel">
            <div class="technology-section__panel-lt">
                <img class="img--sm-box lamplight" src = {ImagesRoute.Blazor_940x940}/>
            </div>
            <div class="technology-section__panel-center">
                <img class="img--sm-box lamplight" src = {ImagesRoute.MAUI}/>
            </div>
            <div class="technology-section__panel-rb">
                <img class="img--sm-box lamplight" src = {ImagesRoute.net_icon}/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    .technology-section{
        display:flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        box-sizing:border-box;
        padding:3rem;

        &__inner{
            display:flex;
            justify-content:space-between;
            align-items:center;
            > *{
                flex:1;
            }
        }
        &__panel{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            &-lt,&-center,&-rb{
                width:100%;
                display: flex;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                padding: 0 3rem;
            }
            &-lt{
                justify-content: start;
                align-items: start;
            }
            &-center{
                justify-content: end;
                align-items: end;
            }
            &-rb{
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    }

    .technology-section > * + *{
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

@media(max-width:1024px){
    .technology-section{
        &__inner{
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        &__panel{
            width: 100%;
        }
    }
}
</style>